Floaty is an app for displaying images, transparently, above other desktop windows.

- Drag and drop images onto the receptacle window (dashed border).

- Images can be resized as you would a standard window

- The opacity of the images can be adjusted using '+' or '-'

- Use '/' to fix the images in place, making them non-interactive. To
  unfix the images simply click on the Floaty program icon

- Supports PNG, JPEG and other standard web browser compatible formats

Floaty requires Electron https://electronjs.org/
